{"tid":1061114,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙利埋怨基輔球場差：球員存受傷風險","createTime":"2019-03-14T07:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:29:44.000Z","uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7c95df16facfa7a0a3772f1ddd07c619fe8ba157","tid":1061114,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:39:17.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=968ce843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】車路士將於周四的歐霸盃16強次回合作客基輔戴拿模，賽前領隊沙利批評基輔球場的狀況，擔心球員在比賽面臨嚴重受傷的風險。<br />\n<br />\n車路士於首回合主場領先3:0，周四次回合作客基輔戴拿模，領隊沙利（Maurizio Sarri）賽前表示擔心奧林匹克國家綜合體育場草地的質素，會令球員受傷。沙利在首次訓練後表現得十分沮喪，並與他的助手進行深入討論。<br />\n<br />\n「這一刻在這裡踢足球真的很危險，我認為有受傷的風險。」沙利說，「但情況就是這樣，所以我們必須接受這種情況，我們必須在這個球場上比賽。」<br />\n<br />\n沙利同時質疑歐洲足協為何允許在這樣的球場比賽，「我無法理解為甚麼歐洲足協會這樣&hellip;&hellip;但你必須在某時間出示球員名單，然後我們必須在如此糟糕的球場上比賽。但情況是這樣的。」"},{"pid":"f1f9f03e0441c203b47e2d2cdaa436fe3f0be6a1","tid":1061114,"uid":10795,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"睇左做沙基利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee041985afa57c24949745065b0790a6d30293c","tid":1061114,"uid":66113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"佢肯定冇聽過史丹福橋薯仔田"},{"pid":"0a4d46d77390fbfbbd3945c437c44e2faee1e4f7","tid":1061114,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f9f03e0441c203b47e2d2cdaa436fe3f0be6a1","tid":1061114,"uid":10795,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"睇左做沙基利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit